     Outreg$0 (Ra) → Inreg$1   add reads Ra as first input
     Outreg$1 (Rb) → Inreg$2   add reads Rb as second input
     Outreg$2 (Rc) → Inaddr$2  load[Rc] uses Rc as its address   -->
<field label="rf" ID="40" parentID="38">
